  "notes": [
    "Adds an exportable Recovery Kit for KmerHosting managed Supabase installations.",
    "Lets the official installer create, recover or permanently delete a managed Supabase installation.",
    "Rotates the recovery key and revokes previous sessions after a successful recovery.",
    "Sends a signed server heartbeat every 12 hours so an unused but running installation remains active.",
    "Freezes managed Supabase data after 30 days without a valid heartbeat or authenticated activity.",
    "Blocks normal login and revokes sessions while a managed instance is frozen.",
    "Permanently deletes managed Supabase records after 90 days without activity or recovery.",
    "Does not send inactivity warning emails or notifications.",
    "Deletes managed Supabase records during uninstall when the Recovery Kit is available."
  ],
